            <fr:p>The hypercohomology spectral sequence (for <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[T]]></fr:tex>) of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[K\in \operatorname {Ob}\mathrm {D}^+\mathrm {F}(\mathscr {A})]]></fr:tex> is the spectral sequence of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathrm {R} TK\in \operatorname {Ob}\mathrm {D}^+\mathrm {F}(\mathscr {B})]]></fr:tex> (cf. <fr:ref addr="hodge-theory-ii-1.4.5" href="hodge-theory-ii-1.4.5.xml" number="1.4.5" />).</fr:p>
